channel.title: The error of -fedexer-'s Global Object Tut! (NOT a compile error)
channel.description: Guys, I used [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,35848.0/topicseen.html]-fedexer-'s Global Object Tutorial[/url]. I compiled and spawn objects successfully. When I spawn the objects, and type the coords in, it appears where I want it to too. BUT sometimes, when I spawn them, the objects appear where I want it to, and in random places too... Like I spawned a portal. It appeared where I want it to. And in another area, I can see another portal in the middle of the ocean... I didn't even spawn it there... does anyone know why this happens, and how I can solve this?
